mlflow-naming-convention.run-naming:
Training: {model}__{loss}__{calib}__{fold}
Post-training: {model}__{loss}__{calib}__{fold}__{method}
where method in {swa, multi_swa, model_soup, calibrated}
This creates new factorial conditions for Biostatistics Flow.

mlflow-naming-convention.tags:

flow_name: "post-training-flow"
upstream_training_run_id: {original_run_id}
post_training_method: {method_name} — "none", "swa", "multi_swa", "calibrated"
model_family: {inherited from upstream}
loss_function: {inherited from upstream}
fold_id: {inherited from upstream}
with_aux_calib: {inherited from upstream}
